Rory McIlroy will be last out on Sunday at Valhalla as he looks to maintain his one-shot lead of the US PGA Championship.

The Northern Irishman, who finished day three on -13, is set to tee off at 14.55 local time (7.55pm in the UK), alongside Bernd Wiesberger. 

